OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FA 50-year-old man who killed a 91-year-
OL,7,Fold veteran after he struck him riding
OL,8,Fhis electric bike on the pavement on
OL,9,Fhis way to work has avoided an
OL,10,Fimmediate jail term.
OL,12,FAt Maidstone Crown Court, Clifford
OL,13,FCage, of The Fairway, Rochester, was
OL,14,Fsentenced to 15 months' imprisonment,
OL,15,Fsuspended for two years.
OL,17,FHe'd previously admitted the charge of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter following the death of
OL,19,FJim Blackwood in 2023.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
