OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fhas described the conviction as one of
OL,8,Fthe first of its kind in the UK
OL,9,Finvolving an e-bike.
OL,11,FWATCH: CCTV footage captures the
OL,12,Fmoment 91-year-old Jim Blackwood was
OL,13,Fstruck by an e-bike while putting out
OL,14,Fhis recycling in Rochester.
OL,16,FThe court heard a statement from Jim
OL,17,FBlackwood's wife of 72 years, Hanni
OL,18,FBlackwood, who said she misses him all
OL,19,Fthe time, adding: "There's not a day I
OL,20,Fdon't think of him".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FShe said as a former Army man, Mr
OL,7,FBlackwood had served in Malaya and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland "but was killed
OL,9,Foutside his front door".
OL,11,FMr Blackwood's daughter, Christine
OL,12,FWhite told of the "huge emotional
OL,13,Ftoll" the incident has had on her and
OL,14,Fsaid she generally "feels angry all
OL,15,Fthe time".
OL,17,F"It's painful to see mum suffering so
OL,18,Fmuch, she really doesn't want to be
OL,19,Fhere without her partner of 72 years,"
OL,20,Fshe said. "I miss dad terribly, I was
OL,21,Fa real daddy's girl."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FLISTEN: "Stay still": Hear the 999
OL,7,Fcall made from the scene in Rochester
OL,8,Fas Clifford Cage sought help for the
OL,9,Finjured 91-year-old.
OL,11,FSentencing Cage, Judge Julian Smith
OL,12,Fsaid Mr Blackwood "suffered
OL,13,Fsignificantly" in his final months,
OL,14,Fadding of the sentence: "That is no
OL,15,Fmeasure of a man's life, but is of Mr
OL,16,FCage's culpability.
OL,18,F"No doubt he should not have been
OL,19,Friding on that path in that way."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FDefending Cage, Danny Moore KC said
OL,7,Fthe grandfather stayed at the scene
OL,8,Fand "did what he could to help" and
OL,9,Fthat "he's a decent human being".
OL,11,FHe said: "He knows a moment of
OL,12,Fcareless driving has resulted in
OL,13,Ftragedy. The knowledge his actions
OL,14,Fhave caused the death of another human
OL,15,Fbeing is something he will carry with
OL,16,Fhim for the rest of his life."
OL,18,FThe judge also ordered for Cage to
OL,19,Fcarry out 15 days of rehabilitative
OL,20,Factivity requirement and 180 hours of
OL,21,Funpaid work.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Cage and Mr
OL,7,FBlackwood's daughter, Christine White,
OL,8,Fhugged in the courtroom.
OL,10,FSpeaking outside court she said the
OL,11,Ffamily had been "floundering" since
OL,12,Fthe loss of the man who was the "hub"
OL,13,Fof their lives: "Dad was a lovely guy.
OL,14,FI fully expected him to get to 100.
OL,16,F"What upset (my mother) the most is
OL,17,Fthe fact that he died literally on his
OL,18,Fown front doorstep. She has found that
OL,19,Freally hard to come to terms with."
OL,26,@xD@MpmxD@Wpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FMs. White described the sentence as
OL,7,F"fair" given the judge's comments, but
OL,8,Fnoted that her father was "unfairly
OL,9,Fand cruelly taken away."
OL,11,FWATCH: Mr Blackwood's daughter
OL,12,FChristine White's statement IN FULL
OL,13,Foutside Maidstone Crown Court
OL,15,FJim Blackwood, a husband, father, and
OL,16,Fgreat-grandfather, was struck by the e-
OL,17,Fbike in July 2023 while he was putting
OL,18,Fhis recycling bins out near his home
OL,19,Fin Rochester.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FMr. Blackwood had been walking back
OL,7,Ftoward his address after placing his
OL,8,Fbins on a grass verge when Cage,
OL,9,Friding on the pavement at
OL,10,F"considerable speed," collided with
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FThough Cage claimed he was traveling
OL,14,Fat 12mph, the CPS noted he was riding
OL,15,Fa silent vehicle and his vision was
OL,16,Fobscured by a large tree.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FThe 91-year-old veteran suffered head
OL,7,Fand kidney injuries that were
OL,8,Finitially not thought to be life-
OL,9,Fthreatening. However, his condition
OL,10,Fdeteriorated days later, and he passed
OL,11,Faway three months after the collision.
OL,13,FWATCH: District Crown Prosecutor Matt
OL,14,FBaird's warning to other cyclists
OL,16,FThe CPS initially considered charging
OL,17,FCage with "wanton and furious driving"
OL,18,F- a law dating back to 1861 - but felt
OL,19,Fit did not reflect the criminality of
OL,20,Fthe incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,FInstead, they sought a manslaughter
OL,7,Fconviction, which District Crown
OL,8,FProsecutor Matt Baird described as a
OL,9,F"quite unusual" but necessary result.
OL,11,F"The legislation as it stands doesn't
OL,12,Faccount for this scenario," Mr. Baird
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Manslaughter is a very serious
OL,16,Fcharge, but on this case, when we
OL,17,Freflect upon it, it was our view that
OL,18,Fit was the right thing to do.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,F"Riding on the pavement is illegal,
OL,7,Fand it's illegal for a reason. The
OL,8,Ftakeaway from this is, if you're on a
OL,9,Fbike, whether it be a normal bike or
OL,10,Fan e-bike, use the road. Don't ride on
OL,11,Fthe pavement, especially not at such
OL,12,Fbreakneck speed."
OL,14,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,15,FConstable Sam Sylvester said: 'This is
OL,16,Fa truly tragic incident that should
OL,17,Fnever have happened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,F"So many lives have been impacted by a
OL,7,Fmomentary lapse of judgement from a
OL,8,Fman who had, prior to this event, only
OL,9,Fdemonstrated good character."
OL,11,FMs. White is now calling for a rethink
OL,12,Fof e-bike laws, including raising the
OL,13,Fminimum age for riders from 14 to 16
OL,14,Fand introducing mandatory licensing or
OL,15,Ftraining.
OL,17,F"With the introduction of electric
OL,18,Fbikes, walking along our pavements has
OL,19,Fbecome dangerous to the point of
OL,20,Fbecoming a lottery," she warned.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773306338
OL,3,CE-bike rider avoids immediate jail for
OL,4,C'landmark' manslaughter of veteran
OL,6,F"No longer can cyclists decide that
OL,7,Fthey can leave the road and ride on
OL,8,Four pavements, endangering pedestrians
OL,9,Fwith impunity."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
